        <ontology:hasDescription>The size of the area (km2) is 3014.41. The minimum altimetry of the LAU (Local Administrative Unit) is 304. The maximum altimetry of the LAU is 1208. The total population (in thousand) is 6.627. The population density (Inhabitants/km2) in the LAU is 2.19. The population change rate of the LAU in the last 10 years (%) has been -2.04%. The overall regional population density (Inhabitants/km2) is 7.13. The regional population change rate in the last 10 years (%) has been 2.86%.  </ontology:hasDescription>
    </NamedIndividual>
    


