        <ontology:hasDescription>The average per capita income (EUR/year) [Province] is 44611.91. The total Gross Value Added (GVA) (EUR million/year) [Province] is 7816.93. The primary sector share of total GVA/year [Province] is 8.44%. The secondary sector share of total GVA/year [Province] is 16.41%. The tertiary sector share of total GVA/year [Province] is 75.14%. The per capita income (EUR/year) [Region] is 46253.25. The total Gross Value Added (GVA) (EUR million/year) [Region] is 15265.23. The primary sector share of total GVA/year [Region] is 3.65%. The secondary sector share of total GVA/year [Region] is 23.37%. The tertiary sector share of total GVA/year [Region] is 72.98%.  </ontology:hasDescription>
    </NamedIndividual>
    


