        <ontology:hasDescription>The total number of bed places (BPs) in tourist accommodations/year in the LAU (Local Administrative Unit) is 2477. The regional (Region) share of total BPs/year is 0.09%. The number of agricultural holdings in the LAU is 3031. The nearest settlement with population over 100000 (km) is 204. In this region protected areas are present.  </ontology:hasDescription>
